full_description:
AMD Ryzen Boxed Cooling Fan Original

AMD Ryzen Boxed Cooling Fans are the Original CPU coolers usually offered with an AMD Ryzen series of processors. This CPU supports the AMD Ryzen family of CPUs. Namely Ryzen 3, Ryzen 5, Ryzen 7, and Ryzen 9. The supported Socket of this cooler is AM4. This cooler has a 90 mm Fan and the size is 90x90x25mm. The CPU fan utilizes a Fluid Bearing. The Fan Life is 100000 hrs and the cooler's Power Interface is a 4pin PWM connector as a Power Interface. it is compatible with any AM4 Socket Compatible Processor. The Heatsink is a specialized AMD CPU Heatsink made with Aluminum. The Aluminium heatsink and 4pin power connector ensure maximum efficiency.
